data.description: WELCOME TO BREMEN, ALABAMA! THIS BARNDOMINUM OFFERS 4200 SQUARE FEET! THIS HOME IS ON OVER 4 ACRES AND ON A PRIVATE LOT AND HAS A VIEW OF THE BEAUTIFUL SMITH LAKE FROM THE BACK YARD! THE LOWER LEVEL IS OPEN-CONCEPT AND THERE IS A LARGE KITCHEN THAT IS VERY FUNCTIONAL FOR HOSTING. THE LARGE KITCHEN ISLAND IS THE FOCAL POINT OF THE AREA AND HAS LOTS OF STORAGE SPACE. THE UPSTAIR LEVEL HOSTS THE 3 BEDROOMS! THERE IS SO MUCH SPACE AND SO MUCH OPPORTUNITY TO MAKE THIS HOME PERFECT FOR YOUR FAMILY OR WEEKEND SPOT! SCHEDULE YOUR SHOWING TODAY!!
